Ughelli- HRM, Godspower Oporomo, the Taraeza 1 of Kerebiri-Mein kingdom in Bomadi Local Government Area of Delta State has appealed to the State Government to do justice and remove them from ungodly oppression and expeditiously recognize the kingdom. The Delta monarch called on Okowa to address issues causing the delay in presentation of staff of office to him, the abandoned Bomadi polytechnic project that was passed by the State House of Assembly and the unfulfilled aged long promise of government to link Bomadi and its environ to national grid. The Taraeza 1 said this in an address during the occasion to mark his fourth coronation anniversary at his palace playground Bomadi also urging the State Governor to consider politicians from his domain vital and appreciable political appointments. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCEÂ DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Speaking further, He alleged undue interference on their lawful and peaceful activities by the Pere of Akugbene Mein Kingdom whom he said has infringed on their rights of association urging the Kerebiri-Mein people to turn down activities of Akugbene -Mein Kingdom for them not to infiltrate into their communities politics. Oporomo said, painstaking approaches were employed by the kingdom to address the omission of their autonomous kingdom in the constitution of Ijaw Youth Congress IYC, and the Ijaw National Congress INC. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION